
    xillatags


        Simple lightweight PHP tag library for generating HTML pages programatically.

        Indented code structure matches structure of the html.

        Functional lisp-flavored, highly nested programming idiom rather than object-oriented?

        Automatically close tags, while maintaining readable PHP code. 


